Created table of Person:
create table IF NOT EXISTS Person (
    person_id BIGINT GENERATED BY DEFAULT AS IDENTITY PRIMARY KEY ,
    full_name varchar(100) UNIQUE  NOT NULL,
    year_of_birth int CHECK ( year_of_birth > 1900 ) NOT NULL
)

Created table of book:
create table Book (
    book_id BIGINT GENERATED BY DEFAULT AS IDENTITY PRIMARY KEY ,
    person_id BIGINT REFERENCES person(person_id),
    book_name varchar(100) UNIQUE NOT NULL,
    author_full_name varchar(100) UNIQUE NOT NULL,
    year_of_pub int CHECK ( year_of_pub > 1700 ) NOT NULL
)

Connected all useful dependencies(postgreSQL, spring core, spring context, spring-web, spring-webmvc, spring-jdbc, thymeleaf-spring5, servlet, hybernate-validator)

Created configuration java-class files for Spring (MyWebAppInitializer, SpringConfig)

Created beans for jdbc template

Created Person class

Created Book class

Created CRUD for Person
